lead_paragraph: Africa could hold the key to FIFA's presidential election, but sharply conflicting versions emerged on Thursday of who would get the continent's 54 votes in the contest for the new head of world soccer.

headline.print_headline: On Eve of FIFA Election, Key African Vote Is Hard to Call
headline.main: On Eve of FIFA Election, Key African Vote Is Hard to Call
